{"tid":1475703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【8.16撳錢圍爐區】巴絲曬錢圖及各區atm停擺情況(+樓主致香港人家書)","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T13:49:57.000Z","uid":193565,"like":154,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"b971b509a612333f62f6351812df7be83d8598d1","tid":1475703,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"歷時兩個月的反送中運動，使港共暴政完完全全暴露於市民眼中，警暴、官商鄉黑合作等令人髮指的行為已經使香港市民對政府完全失去信心，更有消息指中共已經竊取香港的外匯儲備，匯豐高層於中國平安成為大股東後相繼離職，可見中共之惡手已伸延至香港銀行體系，使港人對其信心大降。<br />\n<br />\n觀乎近日中國軍隊於深圳邊境集結，香港市民有理由相信中共可能會以軍隊對港進行鎮壓，屆時人人惶恐、外資撤離。另外，港元一年期權於昨晚已跌穿7.85，證明市場預期港元1年內將會與美元脫鈎，聯繫匯款崩潰，港元勢成廢紙，若要自保，必先將大部份資產轉換成美元或其他可靠外幣，才能保值。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今早再有消息傳出中共望將香港變成直轄市，取消一國兩制，取消港元在港的合法地位，以人民幣進行交易，企圖盡數竊取港人的外匯儲備，升斗市民若要防範魔鬼暴政帶來的資產損失，只能在此時將港元轉換成外匯，手持現鈔，才是真財富，屆時樓價大跌，磚頭亦不保值。<br />\n<br />\n經本人一晚的收集，加上【傾閪咩？】巴打的貼文(<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472715</a>) ，已有超過二百位市民率先將存款提出，港元等值以億計，部分人已開始兌換外幣，本人在此呼籲市民，若要保值，必先提現、兌美金或其他可靠外幣，香港市民的財產不能被共產黨蠶食。市民應以現鈔表態，透過減少銀行現金流，堅決反對中共在港的一切所作所為，並對暴政表示強烈譴責，防止手上資產成為垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8.16撳錢換美金</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Za5NeFs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZa5NeFs.jpg&h=c3caf632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbkA70t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbkA70t.jpg&h=6f1d8583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWqxqNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWqxqNb.jpg&h=81396519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyJvcsd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyJvcsd.jpg&h=21c89bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各區ATM停止港元/美金提款服務：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdLmjr8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwdLmjr8.png&h=895a03e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n以下為整合前原圖及<span style=\"color: red;\">更多</span>ATM停擺圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/10usZILGZnF97BGcoI2CWPazn_QD9jnpg?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F10usZILGZnF97BGcoI2CWPazn_QD9jnpg%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=2c5f85e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/10usZILGZnF97BGcoI2CWPazn_QD9jnpg?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAvA74K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAvA74K.jpg&h=a7f47c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwM8JC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwM8JC4.jpg&h=acef6ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50WQcwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50WQcwp.jpg&h=8e2342b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJENZbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJENZbp.jpg&h=9ccc679c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h3CWSwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh3CWSwq.jpg&h=e0ea0bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3epyah5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3epyah5.jpg&h=24434093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主致香港人的一封家書：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVcoxNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVcoxNL.png&h=a8082be9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n在收集圖片時看到這一張相片，我感到無比心痛，在歷時兩個月的反送中運動當中，我們失去了6個家人的性命，讓年輕人付出未來、流了無數的血，居民因催淚毒氣流了無數的淚，警察失去了人性，香港所有人都是輸家。<br />\n<br />\n我認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">一個人的價值不在於他擁有多少，而在於他肯付出多少</span>，當年輕人為了香港的未來付出所有，卻只換來暴政的打壓，這正是我感到心痛的原因。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個有血性、良知的人，我們要讓港共官員、中共高官知道，香港當家的應是香港人，香港銀行體系的根基是市民，而不是毫無道德意識的高官和中國商人。<br />\n<br />\n8.16撳錢、換美金，願香港變得更好，五大訴求，缺一不可，共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n一名have no stake in society的市民上"},{"pid":"297dea4e19f7fea36987ab24feb75cbf9b46000b","tid":1475703,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f0bcf55d8b9e7361b4488246bcc10c3962555144","tid":1475703,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481c18231f45f9e260a14685b7885289062c59c6","tid":1475703,"uid":193565,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"整得好辛苦，希望有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39166673ff10e4d54738e7cb56f74460536335a3","tid":1475703,"uid":2117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb334ce3ab2d4e0336a6ce525c3bb8c86c65696","tid":1475703,"uid":274136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n長期戰 不氣餒</span></ins></em></strong></span><br />\n唔好意思，阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n香港人重要日程：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月16日</strong>：學界萬人炒聯手萬人集會（2000遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月16日</strong>：大家記得撳錢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>8月17日</strong>：教師大遊行（1100遮打花園）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：光復紅土（1530紅磡馬頭）<br />\n<strong>8月17日</strong>：寵物集會（1930愛丁堡廣場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月18日</strong>：民陣大遊行（1500維園）</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>8月23日</strong>：會計界遊行（1230遮打花園）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月24日</strong>：觀塘大遊行（1300駿業街球場）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>8月25日</strong>：荃葵青遊街（1400葵青劇院集合）</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足，到時見！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a20e8831755a3ecddcc4bd892cc9114e3c920533","tid":1475703,"uid":153260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50edf1972793842b5e38137a989285e49d70e5da","tid":1475703,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5a8d884634d2de9d28369e788f06583c810ea7","tid":1475703,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"915a0b95caaed2a770c5b7a089d107b64aa25e95","tid":1475703,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"33fe3c2e54cc2731f4c52de8b5c0060910eea752","tid":1475703,"uid":261169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"撳錢撳錢撳錢"},{"pid":"5cf3f0a5cd387132e9e05f418cbec8bdaf652e97","tid":1475703,"uid":276150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"攞錢同入銀行排隊一樣咁緊要！排隊！影相！"},{"pid":"69005b6cf5d6af4aeff4064a4f28b329a784e5c5","tid":1475703,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/